additionalProperty.name: Warning
additionalProperty.value: Use only as directed. Keep out of reach of children and pets. May cause sensitisation by skin contact. People suffering from perfume sensitivity should be cautious when using this product. Avoid contact with skin and eyes. Always switch off at the socket before removing or inserting fragrance refill. Do not place in an area where the diffuser may be susceptible to hard knocks. Always keep the bottle and/or diffuser in an upright position. This product should not be used continuously, always switch off overnight. Prolonged use in one socket is not recommended.
